data.title: Emigration from the Scandinavian Mission
data.text:
Emigration from the LDS Scandinavian Mission 1854-1868

Always refer to the original record on LDS microfilm 025696 to verify this information.

The list is sorted by surname, first name

Those who were under 12 months old were rounded up to 1 year of age.

Those of unknown age have an age of 0.

The people who had their names crossed out were presumably not migrating at that time and are not included on this list. See the original record for these names.

A new field, "Register Page" has been added, which indicates the page in the emigration register where the entry was found. The page numbering re-starts for the years 1864, 1866, 1867. Families are usually listed together on the same page.
